<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
<title>AI Search Readiness Audit — {{domain}}</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0b0d12;
    --panel: #11141b;
    --panel-2: #161a23;
    --ink: #e7ebf3;
    --ink-dim: #9aa3b2;
    --accent: #7c5cff;
    --accent-2: #22d3ee;
    --good: #34d399;
    --warn: #fbbf24;
    --bad: #f87171;
    --line: #232838;
    --radius: 14px;
  }
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: light) {
    :root {
      --bg: #f7f8fb;
      --panel: #ffffff;
      --panel-2: #f1f3f8;
      --ink: #11141b;
      --ink-dim: #5a6275;
      --line: #e4e7ef;
    }
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  html, body { background: var(--bg); color: var(--ink); margin: 0; }
  body {
    font: 15px/1.55 -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Inter", "Segoe UI", system-ui, sans-serif;
    padding: 40px 24px 80px;
  }
  .wrap { max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; }
  header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; gap: 24px; margin-bottom: 28px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  header h1 { font-size: 28px; margin: 0 0 6px; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
  header .meta { color: var(--ink-dim); font-size: 13px; }
  header .brand { font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink-dim); text-align: right; }
  header .brand a { color: var(--accent-2); text-decoration: none; }

  .hero {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 260px 1fr; gap: 24px;
    background: var(--panel); border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 28px; margin-bottom: 20px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  @media (max-width: 760px) { .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .gauge { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
  .gauge .ring {
    --size: 220px; --val: {{site_score}};
    width: var(--size); height: var(--size); border-radius: 50%;
    background: conic-gradient(var(--accent) calc(var(--val) * 3.6deg), var(--panel-2) 0);
    display: grid; place-items: center; position: relative;
  }
  .gauge .ring::before {
    content: ""; width: 76%; height: 76%; background: var(--panel); border-radius: 50%; position: absolute;
  }
  .gauge .num { position: relative; font-size: 72px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.03em; line-height: 1; }
  .gauge .num small { font-size: 20px; color: var(--ink-dim); font-weight: 500; }
  .gauge .label { margin-top: 12px; color: var(--ink-dim); font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; font-weight: 600; }

  .headline { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; }
  .headline strong { color: var(--accent-2); }

  /* F1 dimension chips */
  .dims { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr); gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  @media (max-width: 760px) { .dims { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
  .dim {
    background: var(--panel); border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 16px 14px;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .dim::before {
    content: ""; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px;
    background: var(--line);
  }
  .dim.p-max::before { background: var(--good); }
  .dim.p-good::before { background: var(--accent-2); }
  .dim.p-mid::before  { background: var(--warn); }
  .dim.p-low::before  { background: var(--bad); }
  .dim .name { font-size: 10px; color: var(--ink-dim); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; font-weight: 700; }
  .dim .val {
    font-size: 36px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 10px 0 2px; line-height: 1; color: var(--ink-dim);
  }
  .dim.p-max .val { color: var(--good); }
  .dim.p-good .val { color: var(--accent-2); }
  .dim.p-mid  .val { color: var(--warn); }
  .dim.p-low  .val { color: var(--bad); }
  .dim .val small { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink-dim); }
  .dim .bar { display: none; }
  .dim .blocker { font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink-dim); margin-top: 8px; line-height: 1.45; }

  section.card {
    background: var(--panel); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 22px 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  section.card h2 { font-size: 18px; margin: 0 0 14px; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }

  .fixes { display: grid; gap: 10px; }
  .fix { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 28px 1fr auto; gap: 12px; align-items: center; padding: 12px; background: var(--panel-2); border-radius: 10px; }
  .fix .rank { font-weight: 700; color: var(--accent); font-size: 16px; }
  .fix .text { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; }
  .fix .meta { font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink-dim); white-space: nowrap; }
  .pill { display: inline-block; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 999px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; }
  .pill.s { background: rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.15); color: var(--good); }
  .pill.m { background: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.18); color: var(--warn); }
  .pill.l { background: rgba(248, 113, 113, 0.18); color: var(--bad); }

  .buckets { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 10px; }
  @media (max-width: 760px) { .buckets { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
  .bucket { background: var(--panel-2); border-radius: 10px; padding: 14px; text-align: center; }
  .bucket .b-num { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; }
  .bucket .b-label { font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink-dim); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; margin-top: 4px; }
  .bucket.strong .b-num { color: var(--good); }
  .bucket.decent .b-num { color: var(--accent-2); }
  .bucket.weak .b-num { color: var(--warn); }
  .bucket.invisible .b-num { color: var(--bad); }

  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 13px; }
  table th, table td { text-align: left; padding: 10px 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
  table th { font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink-dim); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; font-weight: 600; }
  table tbody tr:hover { background: var(--panel-2); }
  table td.score { font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; font-weight: 600; }
  table td.score.bad { color: var(--bad); }
  table td.score.warn { color: var(--warn); }
  table td.score.good { color: var(--good); }
  table td a { color: var(--accent-2); text-decoration: none; word-break: break-all; }

  .artifacts { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 10px; }
  @media (max-width: 760px) { .artifacts { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .artifact { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; padding: 12px 14px; background: var(--panel-2); border-radius: 10px; font-size: 13px; }
  .artifact .ico { width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 8px; background: var(--accent); display: grid; place-items: center; color: #fff; font-weight: 700; font-size: 12px; }
  .artifact code { background: transparent; color: var(--ink-dim); font-size: 12px; }

  footer { text-align: center; color: var(--ink-dim); font-size: 12px; margin-top: 32px; }
  footer a { color: var(--accent-2); text-decoration: none; }

  @media print {
    body { padding: 0; }
    .wrap { max-width: none; }
    section.card, .hero, .dim { break-inside: avoid; box-shadow: none; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">

  <header>
    <div>
      <h1>AI Search Readiness Audit</h1>
      <div class="meta">{{domain}} · crawled {{crawl_date}} · {{urls_crawled}} URLs · JS rendering {{js_rendering}}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="brand">
      generated by <a href="https://github.com/{{repo_owner}}/ai-search-auditor">ai-search-auditor</a><br>
      <span>Screaming Frog MCP · Claude</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="hero">
    <div class="gauge">
      <div class="ring"><div class="num">{{site_score}}<small>/100</small></div></div>
      <div class="label">Site score</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div style="font-size:11px; color: var(--ink-dim); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin-bottom: 8px;">Headline finding</div>
      <p class="headline"><strong>{{headline_gap}}</strong> {{headline_consequence}} {{headline_action}}</p>
      <div style="margin-top: 14px; font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink-dim);">Top-50 most-linked pages average <strong style="color: var(--ink);">{{top50_avg}}/100</strong>.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="dims">
    <div class="dim">
      <div class="name">Bot Access</div>
      <div class="val">{{bot_access}}<small>/20</small></div>
      <div class="bar"><span style="width: {{bot_access_pct}}%"></span></div>
      <div class="blocker">{{bot_access_blocker}}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="dim">
      <div class="name">Discovery</div>
      <div class="val">{{discovery}}<small>/20</small></div>
      <div class="bar"><span style="width: {{discovery_pct}}%"></span></div>
      <div class="blocker">{{discovery_blocker}}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="dim">
      <div class="name">Structure</div>
      <div class="val">{{structure}}<small>/20</small></div>
      <div class="bar"><span style="width: {{structure_pct}}%"></span></div>
      <div class="blocker">{{structure_blocker}}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="dim">
      <div class="name">Citability</div>
      <div class="val">{{citability}}<small>/20</small></div>
      <div class="bar"><span style="width: {{citability_pct}}%"></span></div>
      <div class="blocker">{{citability_blocker}}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="dim">
      <div class="name">Authority</div>
      <div class="val">{{authority}}<small>/20</small></div>
      <div class="bar"><span style="width: {{authority_pct}}%"></span></div>
      <div class="blocker">{{authority_blocker}}</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {{delta_html}}

  <script>
  (function() {
    var dims = document.querySelectorAll('.dim');
    dims.forEach(function(el) {
      var val = parseInt(el.querySelector('.val').textContent, 10);
      var pct = val / 20;
      if (pct >= 1)        el.classList.add('p-max');
      else if (pct >= 0.7) el.classList.add('p-good');
      else if (pct >= 0.4) el.classList.add('p-mid');
      else                 el.classList.add('p-low');
    });
  })();
  </script>

  <section class="card">
    <h2>Top 5 fixes that move the needle</h2>
    <div class="fixes">{{fixes_html}}</div>
  </section>

  <section class="card">
    <h2>Page buckets</h2>
    <div class="buckets">
      <div class="bucket strong"><div class="b-num">{{bucket_strong}}</div><div class="b-label">Strong 80–100</div></div>
      <div class="bucket decent"><div class="b-num">{{bucket_decent}}</div><div class="b-label">Decent 60–79</div></div>
      <div class="bucket weak"><div class="b-num">{{bucket_weak}}</div><div class="b-label">Weak 40–59</div></div>
      <div class="bucket invisible"><div class="b-num">{{bucket_invisible}}</div><div class="b-label">Invisible 0–39</div></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="card">
    <h2>Priority fix list — top pages below Decent (&lt; 60) by inlink count</h2>
    <table>
      <thead><tr><th>URL</th><th>Inlinks</th><th>Score</th><th>Top miss</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>{{priority_rows_html}}</tbody>
    </table>
  </section>

  <section class="card">
    <h2>Generated artifacts</h2>
    <div class="artifacts">{{artifacts_html}}</div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    Re-audit in 4 weeks after shipping the top fixes. Expected post-fix site score:
    <strong style="color: var(--ink);">{{expected_post_fix_score}}/100</strong>.
    <br>
    Rubric: <a href="https://github.com/{{repo_owner}}/ai-search-auditor/blob/main/.claude/skills/ai-search-audit/rubric.md">deterministic, auditable</a> · v{{rubric_version}}.
    <br style="margin-bottom: 6px;">
    <span style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink-dim); max-width: 700px; display: inline-block; margin-top: 8px; line-height: 1.5;">
      Scope: optimized for citations in ChatGPT, Claude, and Perplexity.
      For Google AI Overviews, <a href="https://developers.google.com/search/docs/fundamentals/ai-optimization-guide" style="color: var(--ink-dim);">Google's own guidance</a> prioritizes foundational SEO over llms.txt and structured data -- use Search Console for Google AI signals.
    </span>
  </footer>

</div>
</body>
</html>
